text.section:
By resolution, the governing body of any municipality may authorize the issuance of bonds under this subtitle to finance, wholly or partly, the cost of the development of any sewerage facility. In the determination of the cost, the governing body may include:
Actual and estimated costs of issuing the bonds;
Engineering expenses;
Inspection expenses;
Fiscal expenses;
Legal expenses; and
Interest estimated to accrue, during construction and for 6 months after construction, on money borrowed or expected to be borrowed under this subtitle.
